description: Global Fiber Technologies, Inc., a development stage fiber rejuvenation technology company, focuses on providing branded fabrics, apparels, and uniforms to the corporate, hotel, hospital, and military markets. The company was formerly known as Eco Tek 360, Inc. and changed its name to Global Fiber Technologies, Inc. in January 2017. Global Fiber Technologies, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is based in Somerset, New Jersey.
